    "summary": "The user asks for help identifying and fixing passive voice in academic writing. The assistant initially responds with a grammar lesson that includes an unprompted goblin metaphor. When the user explicitly asks to stop the metaphors and stick to the technical side, the assistant complies and provides a standard, helpful grammar guide for the remainder of the conversation.",
